{"tid":1721653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好以為又解鎖左成就好開心！","createTime":"2019-11-14T17:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:08:14.000Z","uid":231007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c75af1e9939dff6074f9d74a07332d3072426ac5","tid":1721653,"uid":231007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"大佬呀！我地呢家係打緊仗唔係打機<br />\n雖然有好多新武器魔法好勁<br />\n但講真唔係每個人識用，方唔方便用都好重要<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議繼續做番火水魔法，或者近距離攻擊武器<br />\n新野你未試過一定有風險 <br />\n唔係話研發新野唔好，但都要考慮其他手足<br />\n唔可以得把姐同狗搏命，比人捉到都要有機會甩身<br />\n<br />\nd磚頭牆真係好壯觀啦，但夠唔夠堅固？<br />\n如果d狗開裝甲車一衝就散 真係比人笑9我地<br />\n哂時間哂精神仲浪費哂我地d武器！<br />\n<br />\n呢家已經進入左運動的白熱化階段<br />\n每做一步對運動的成敗都好大影響<br />\n我希望各位手足勇武之前要諗遠d實際d<br />\n我唔想你地白白送頭！<br />\n<br />\n以上只係小小意見 <br />\n見到各位手足咁有創意同努力我真係好佩服<br />\n所以更加唔想浪費你地一番心機<br />\n香港人 反抗！<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"21c6e345f8d3ffc93e2bc1a8d52c0537f3ab27b5","tid":1721653,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter吹大雞！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">！！！McConnell支持法案，重點推 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc65hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1ff25019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&h=8c1d25b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick 多謝 McConnell <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc65hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D